go to promox shell 
create directiory whatever you need
mkdir /media/movies
chmod 775 /media/movies

then edit the container or vm   number config .  e.g 103.conf
nano /etc/pve/local/lxc/103.conf
   append the below line
   mp0: /media/movies/, mp=/media/movies
   then restart the lxc container or vm machine 
   
